{"comments":"BorderImage - image-based border specification.\n\nCSS border-image allows using an image (or gradient) as the border,\nwith control over how it's sliced, scaled, and repeated.\n\n## CSS Border-Image Properties\n\n- **source**: Image URL or gradient\n- **slice**: How to cut the image into 9 regions (4 corners, 4 edges, center)\n- **width**: Width of the border image area\n- **outset**: How far the border extends beyond the border box\n- **repeat**: How edge regions are scaled (stretch, repeat, round, space)\n\n## The 9-Slice Model\n\n```\n┌───────┬───────────────┬───────┐\n│ TL    │     TOP       │    TR │\n├───────┼───────────────┼───────┤\n│ LEFT  │    CENTER     │ RIGHT │\n├───────┼───────────────┼───────┤\n│ BL    │    BOTTOM     │    BR │\n└───────┴───────────────┴───────┘\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Bounded\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderImage.purs","start":[84,3]},"title":"Stretch"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderImage.purs","start":[85,3]},"title":"Repeat"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderImage.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"Round"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BorderImage.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"Space"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BorderImage"],"BorderImageRepeat"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeAp